	<div class="m4col wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".1s"><li id="text-3" class="widget-container widget_text"><h3 class="widget-title"><span>ABOUT US</span></h3>			<div class="textwidget"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-5358" src="https://www.medicoswab.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/MEIDIKE-GENE-LOGO-2.png" alt="" width="80" height="50" /><br />
Medico Technology Co., Ltd. is a professional medical supplies manufacturer from China. We specialize in the production and sales of specimen collection swabs, in-vitro diagnostic kits, CHG antiseptic swabs, applicators, and other related products. We also offer OEM and ODM services. Welcome to inquire and place orders.</p>
